        <Parent_String>houses by form: plan [300005459], houses by form [300122205], houses [300005433], dwellings [300005425], residential structures [300257729], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
